# === Class: PhaseDiagramSummary ===
effortless-ntwf:PhaseDiagramSummary a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "PhaseDiagramSummary" ;
    rdfs:comment "Table: PhaseDiagramSummary — one row summarising the SyntheticPhase grid. Witnesses that all five DistortionType cells (A, B, C+, C-, D) are nonempty in parameter space." .

